<h3>This activities can roughly be grouped. in</h3>

<ol>
  <li>activity before or to prepare customer contact</li>
  <li>supporting customer contact, suporting sales</li>
  <li>support after sales contact</li>
  <li>control, supervising, optimizing the process</li>
  <li>after printing the documents: bookkeeping</li>
  <li>others</li>
</ol>

