<hr>

<p><strong>Note</strong>: <small>A checklist is NOT, however, a specification. Evaluators
should not take the attitude that they will evaluate an item in accordance with or against
the checklist. The checklist is used to ensure thoroughness and consistency in the
assessment. It does not indicate what constitutes compliance</small>.</p>
